      %section#testimonials.section.section-center.section-testimonial
        .container
          %h2.section-title
            %span What are people saying?
          %i.fa.fa-quote-left.fa-3x
          #carousel-example-generic.carousel.slide{"data-ride" => "carousel"}
            .carousel-inner
              .item.active
                %blockquote
                  %p One of the best tents I have ever used, and the whole process was so easy and simple!

              .item
                %blockquote
                  %p A big group of us from work were taking an overnight trip to Yosemite and feeling overwhelmed by the hours of planning and costs of everything. Fortunately, we discovered LMG and got some great advice from James, an outdoor pro. He asked the right questions and gave very sensible advice on what to bring and not to bring. Honestly, James and LMG made this trip a piece of cake. Six stars!
              .item
                %blockquote
                  %p We didn't own what we needed & friends didn't have much to spare. It was super simple to get quality camping supplies from Last Minute Gear; we had a blast on our trip!
            %ol.carousel-indicators
              %li.active{"data-slide-to" => "0", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
                = image_tag "profiles/teresa.jpg", height: 64, width: 64, class: "img-circle"
              %li{"data-slide-to" => "1", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
                = image_tag "profiles/david.jpg", height: 64, width: 64, class: "img-circle"
              %li{"data-slide-to" => "2", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
                = image_tag "profiles/dusty.jpg", height: 64, width: 64, class: "img-circle"
